If you use any of the tools included in RTWTools in any academic work then please cite it as below:

Wilson, R. T, 2013, RTWTools for ENVI, Available at http://rtwilson.com/academic/rtwtools

In BibTeX format:

@electronic{,
  author = {Wilson, R. T.},
  year = {2013},
  title = {RTWTools for ENVI},
  url = {http://rtwilson.com/academic/rtwtools}
}
